I"#<blockquote>
  <p>MVVM way to structure code<br />
<strong>MVVM(Model View View-Model)</strong>은 내가 가장 선호하는 architectural design pattern이다.</p>
  <blockquote>
    <p><strong>MVVM 아키텍쳐의 특징</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>UI components are kept away from the business logic</li>
      <li>Business logic is kept away from the database operations</li>
      <li>Easy to understand and read</li>
      <li>A lot less to worry when it comes to managing life cycle events</li>
    </ol>
  </blockquote>
</blockquote>
